trans-unit.source: Represents a declaration for a method of a type.
<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> can be used to represent the declaration for a method.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> 可以用于表示一种方法的声明。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.ReturnType%2A> property specifies the data type of the method's return value.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.ReturnType%2A>属性指定方法的返回值的数据类型。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Parameters%2A> property contains the method's parameters.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Parameters%2A>属性包含此方法的参数。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Statements%2A> property contains the statements of the method.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Statements%2A>属性包含的方法的语句。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates use of a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> to declare a method that accepts a parameter and returns a value.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示使用<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>声明接受参数并返回一个值的方法。

This constructor creates an empty <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> object.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数创建一个空<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>对象。

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows the use of the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.%23ctor%2A> constructor to create a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> instance.
trans-unit.target: 下面的代码示例演示了利用<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.%23ctor%2A>构造函数来创建<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>实例。

trans-unit.source: This example is part of a larger example provided for the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeGenerator.GenerateCodeFromMember%2A> method.

trans-unit.source: Gets the data types of the interfaces implemented by this method, unless it is a private method implementation, which is indicated by the <see cref="P:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.PrivateImplementationType" /> property.
A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceCollection" /> that indicates the interfaces implemented by this method.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceCollection" /> ，该值指示此方法实现的接口。

trans-unit.source: The types referenced by this collection must consist of interfaces.
trans-unit.target: 引用此集合的类型必须包含的接口。

trans-unit.source: If this <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> represents a declaration for a public method, and this method implements a method on an interface, the interface or interfaces this method implements a method of should be referenced in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 如果此<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>表示的声明的公共方法，并且接口，此方法实现的方法的接口的接口上的方法应在此集合中引用此方法实现。

trans-unit.source: The method should still have the same name as the method of the interface that is implemented by this method.
trans-unit.target: 该方法仍应该具有与此方法实现的接口的方法相同的名称。

trans-unit.source: For some languages, like C#, this has no effect on the syntax.
trans-unit.target: 对于某些语言，如 C# 中，此项的语法上不起作用。

trans-unit.source: For others, like Visual Basic, there is a special syntax for implementing interfaces.
trans-unit.target: 对于其他操作系统，如 Visual Basic 中，没有用于实现接口的特殊的语法。

trans-unit.source: If the method is privately implementing a single interface, the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.PrivateImplementationType%2A> property should be used instead.
trans-unit.target: 如果方法私有实现一个接口，<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.PrivateImplementationType%2A>应改用属性。

trans-unit.source: Gets the parameter declarations for the method.
A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection" /> that indicates the method parameters.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection" /> ，该值指示方法参数。

trans-unit.source: An event that will be raised the first time the <see cref="P:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.ImplementationTypes" /> collection is accessed.
An event that will be raised the first time the <see cref="P:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Parameters" /> collection is accessed.
An event that will be raised the first time the <see cref="P:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Statements" /> collection is accessed.
Gets or sets the data type of the interface this method, if private, implements a method of, if any.

A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference" /> that indicates the data type of the interface with the method that the private method whose declaration is represented by this <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod" /> implements.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference" />指示使用方法的接口的数据类型，表示其声明为私有方法<see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod" />实现。

trans-unit.source: If this <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> represents the declaration of a private method and the method implements a method of an interface, this property should indicate the interface type that the method is implementing a method of.
trans-unit.target: 如果此<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>表示的声明一个私有方法和方法的实现方法的接口，此属性应指示方法正在实现的方法的接口类型。

trans-unit.source: The type referenced by this property must be an interface.
trans-unit.target: 此属性所引用的类型必须是接口。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the data type of the return value of the method.
A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference" /> that indicates the data type of the value returned by the method.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference" /> ，该值指示该方法返回的值的数据类型。

trans-unit.source: Gets the custom attributes of the return type of the method.
A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclarationCollection" /> that indicates the custom attributes.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclarationCollection" /> ，该值指示自定义属性。

trans-unit.source: Gets the statements within the method.
A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeStatementCollection" /> that indicates the statements within the method.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeStatementCollection" /> ，该值指示方法内的语句。

trans-unit.source: Gets the type parameters for the current generic method.
A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameterCollection" /> that contains the type parameters for the generic method.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameterCollection" />包含泛型方法的类型参数。

trans-unit.source: A generic method contains one or more unspecified types known as type parameters.
trans-unit.target: 泛型方法包含一个或多个未指定名为类型参数的类型。

trans-unit.source: A type parameter name stands for the type within the body of the generic declaration.
trans-unit.target: 类型参数名称代表泛型声明主体中的类型。

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows the use of the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.TypeParameters%2A> property to add two type parameters to the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> `printMethod`.
trans-unit.target: 下面的代码示例演示了利用<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.TypeParameters%2A>属性添加到两个类型参数<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> `printMethod`。

trans-unit.source: This example is part of a larger example provided for the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameter> class.
trans-unit.target: 此示例摘自更大的示例为提供<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameter>类。
